definition: first month of the lunar year
straight/upright/proper/main/principal/to correct/to rectify/exactly/just (at that time)/right (in that place)/(math.) positive
exactly/in good order/whole/complete/entire/in order/orderly/to repair/to mend/to renovate/(coll.) to fix sb/to give sb a hard time/to mess with sb

sentences.english: a to the b where b is an integer.
sentences.chinese: 也就是a的b次方，而b是個正整數。

sentences.english: An example of semigroup with no minimal ideal is the set of positive integers under addition.
sentences.chinese: 沒有極小理想的半羣的例子是在加法下的正整數集合。

sentences.english: A composite is a positive integer with more than two divisors.
sentences.chinese: 複合數就是具有一個以上約數的正整數。

sentences.english: Scale maximum must be a positive integer value.
sentences.chinese: 比例最大值必須是一個正整數。

sentences.english: Every positive integer greater than 1 can be expressed as the product of prime numbers.
sentences.chinese: 每個大於1的正整數都能表示爲素數的乘積。

sentences.english: The second line of each test case will contain a permutation of the N smallest positive integers.
sentences.chinese: 每個測試案例第二行包含了N最小的正整數置換。

sentences.english: How many four-digit positive integers have their product of digits even?
sentences.chinese: 數字之積爲偶數的四位正整數共有多少個？

sentences.english: I demand that you give me a positive integer.
sentences.chinese: 我要求你給我一個正整數。

sentences.english: The sum of two positive integers is 29, find the minimum value of the sum of their squares.
sentences.chinese: 兩個正整數之和爲29，求此兩數平方和的最小值。

sentences.english: Each transmitter will be assigned one positive integer channel.
sentences.chinese: 每一個傳送站將被配置一正整數信道。

sentences.english: In arithmetic the positive integer and the positive fraction were sufficient for all requirements.
sentences.chinese: 在算數中，曾經正整數和正分數能夠滿足所有的需求。
